title: マヌ～ルのゆうべ
description: hin the nature "Darwin Kita! Kikimono Shin Densetsu" program on NHK1.5 airs the short Manul no Yuube , based on a web manga/comic of the same name. It following animal characters who visit the bar Manul no Yuube . The bar is run by the Mama who is a Pallas's cat ( Otocolobus manul ) and serviced by the hostess Tsunomin who is a Brazilian treehopper ( Bocydium globulare ).
